parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the passenger air bag sensor can cause the air bag to not deploy in the event of a crash, which can lead to serious injury or death.
symptoms: The passenger air bag light is on
the air bag warning light illuminates
the air bag does not deploy in a crash
the passenger seat air bag sensor is faulty
the air bag system is malfunctioning.
